
                       geant4-10-03-ref-00
                       ===================

Major development/fixes included since the last development tag are:

 o Added Extent() virtual method to G4VSolid and derived solids, to
   better factorise code for CalculateExtent(), and completed migration
   of implementation to G4BoundingEnvelope.
 o Fixed initialisation of de-excitation module per geometrical region.
 o Added G4VMoleculeCounter in G4DNA and enabled using custom molecule counter.
 o Reverted implementation to "stable" version for parton-string hadronic model,
   corresponding to version included in releae 10.2.p02, with G4FTFModel and
   residual nucleus excitation energy for diffraction as in release 10.1.
 o New G4FastSimulationManagerHelper utility, used for adding
   G4FastSimulationManagerProcess to a process manager.
 o Create unique names with logical-volume pointer for G4MultiSensitiveDetector
   and avoid to register target sensitive-detector implictly.
 o Enabled auto-update widget for commands in Qt UI.
 o Updated G4Py for release and its build scripts.
 o Completed porting on MacOS Sierra (XCode 8.x) and clang-3.9.
 o Updated data sets G4RadioactiveDecay-5.1, G4PhotonEvaporation-4.3,
   G4ENSDFSTATE-2.1 and G4TENDL-1.3.
 o Updated to CLHEP-2.3.4.3.

---------- Reference-tag 'Release Notes' -----------

(*)  Fixes included in release 10.2.p03

Summarised, the list of changes is the following:

cmake                                            cmake-V10-02-37
-----
- Change default build type to Release when using single mode tools like
  Make/Ninja.
- Fix bug in Qt4/5 handling on Windows. Added expansion variable for Qt
  dynamic loader setup and fixed export of Qt settings to GNUmake
  configuration scripts.
- Added FindDCMTK.cmake needed for extended/medical/DICOM example.
- Correctly export USolids/VecGeom settings to GNUmake configuration scripts.(*)
- Fixed optimization level in Release mode for Windows to be -Ox.
- Always convert exported data paths to native CMake paths. Prevents parse
  errors on Windows, where native paths are exported.
- Updated to data sets G4RadioactiveDecay-5.1, G4PhotonEvaporation-4.3,
  G4ENSDFSTATE-2.1 and G4TENDL-1.3.

config                                           config-V10-02-07
------
- Added include path for analysis/accumulables sub-module.

environments                                     envs-V10-02-02
------------
- G4Py: updated for release 10.3.
- Modified CMake scripts for unit/integration tests with CTest.

analysis                                         analysis-V10-02-25
--------
- Updated to g4tools 2.3.0.
- Added prefix, postfix increment operators to G4Accumulable.
- Added methods to tools/impi for passing ntuple data.
- Fixed Coverity defects.

digits_hits                                      digits_hits-V10-02-10
-----------
- Removed implicit addition to manager of sensitive-detector passed via
  G4MultiSensistiveDetector proxy.
  Addressing problem report #1908.

event                                            event-V10-02-09
-----
- Set polarization to pre-assigned decay products in G4PrimaryTransformer.   (*)
  Addressing problem report #1914.

externals                                        externals-V10-02-11
---------
- Updated to CLHEP-2.3.4.3.
  Fixed array initialisation in Evaluator static method function().

geometry
--------
- magneticfield (field-V10-02-25)
  o Added initialization of fAuxStepper in constructor of 
    G4DoLoMcPriRK34, G4DormandPrince745 & G4DormandPrinceRK56.
  o Fixed G4ClassicalRK4 header with protection against multiple inclusions. (*)
  o Checked while-do loops against potential infinite loops.
- management (geommng-V10-02-26):
  o Added Extent() virtual method to G4VSolid and G4ReflectedSolid.
  o Fixed use of iterator in G4LogicalVolume::ClearDaughters(); simplified   (*)
    implementation.
  o Added new functions SphereExtent(), TriangulatePolygon(), IsConvex(),
    DistancePointSegment() and RemoveRedundantVertices() to G4GeomTools class.
  o Modified G4LogicalCrystalVolume to use G4CrystalExtension.
    Fixed header inclusions and make use of dynamic_cast instead of C-style
    cast; code formatting.
- navigation (geomnav-V10-02-21):                                            (*)
  o Fixed recursion test for overlaps in G4GeomTestVolume to iterate on
    all daughters.
- solids/Boolean (geom-bool-V10-02-11)
  o Implemented Extent() method for all constructs and use it in
    CalculateExtent().
- solids/CSG (geom-csg-V10-02-15):
  o Re-implemented CalculateExtent() to make use of G4BoundingEnvelope and
    removed no-longer used method CreateRotatedVertices() in G4Sphere, G4OTubs,
    G4Torus, G4Orb, and related USolids wrappers.
  o Use G4GeomTools::DiskExtent() for calculation of bounding box in Extent()
    for G4Tubs, G4Cons and related USolids wrappers.
  o Use G4RandFlat instead of RandFlat.                                      (*)
  o Disabled check for intersection of cut planes in G4CutTubs constructor,  (*)
    as too strict and not necessary. Addressing problem report #1887.
  o Added optional debug flag G4BBOX_EXTENT in Extent() for most shapes
    to compare extent calculation by simply using bounding-box.
    Added consistency checks for extent computation in USolids wrappers.
- solids/specific (geom-specific-V10-02-25)
  o Re-implemented CalculateExtent() to make use of G4BoundingEnvelope and
    removed no-longer used method CreateRotatedVertices() in G4Polyhedra,
    G4EllipticalCone, G4Polycone, G4Paraboloid, G4ExtrudedSolid, G4Hype,
    G4GenericPolycone, G4TessellatedSolid, G4TwistedTubs and related USolids
    wrappers.
  o Added caching of corners and implementation of GetCorner() in G4UPolycone
    in order to assure correct translation.
  o G4UPolyhedra extended wrapper to cache corners and start/end Phi
    parameters, to assure correct treatment of angles.
  o Added optional debug flag G4BBOX_EXTENT in Extent() for most solids
    to compare extent calculation by simply using bounding-box.
    Added consistency checks for extent computation in USolids wrappers.
  o Fix in G4PolyPhiFace for potential unitialised data in Inside().
  o Correction in G4EllipticalCone::DistanceToOut(p) to make it more accurate.
  o Use G4RandFlat instead of RandFlat.                                      (*)

