processes/hadronic
------------------
- models/cascade (hadr-casc-V10-02-05)
  o G4InuclCollider: fixed case of segmentation-fault in photonuclearOkay().
    Addressing problem report #1883.
- models/de_excitation (hadr-deex-V10-02-69)
  o Added interface for correlated gamma emission simulation; added ability
    to sample correlated gamma emission in G4PhotonEvaporation and
    G4GammaTransition (not enabled by default).
  o G4ExcitationHandler, G4NeutronRadCapture, G4PhotonEvaporation: use recent
    interface to GetIon().
  o G4LevelReader, G4NuclearLevelData, G4DeexPrecoParameters: enabled
    possibility to read new data files for gamma emission.
  o G4FermiBreakUpVI, G4FermiFragmentsPoolVI: simplified run time
    applicability check
  o G4DeexPrecoParameters: extended initialisation printout.
- models/inclxx (hadr-inclxx-V10-02-05)
  o Updated to INCL++ v5.3: better N-induced eta production cross-sections.
    Modified INCLXXInterface.
- models/lend (hadr-lend-V10-02-06)                                          (*)
  o Improved memory consumption in multi-threaded runs.
  o Fixed compilation warning in GCC with -O3 optimisation option.
- models/lepto_nuclear (hadr-lepnuc-V10-02-03)
  o G4MuonVDNuclearModel: fixed Coverity defect, reduced number of
    bins for transfer energy from 1000 to 800.
- models/particle_hp (hadr-hpp-V10-02-33)
  o Changed default behavior to "DO_NOT_SET_PHP_AS_HP" mode; old behavior
    can be set by setting environment flag "PHP_AS_HP"
    Fixed problem of uninitialisation of cache in G4ParticleHPContAngularPar
    happening for "DO_NOT_SET_PHP_AS_HP" mode; fixed case of infinite loop.
    Fixed also problem of divide by zero error BuildByInterpolation().
  o Fixed wrong residual in case of He3 projectile.
    Addressing problem report #1906.
  o Fixed problem of divide by zero error in G4ParticleHPVector::ThinOut().
  o Reintroduced cache of cross-section in GetIsoCrossSection().             (*)
  o Added protection with flag G4PHP_DO_NOT_ADJUST_FINAL_STATE to
    G4ParticleHPInelasticBaseFS.
- models/parton_string (hadr-prtn-V10-02-03)
  o Reverted implementation to "stable" version, corresponding to version
    included in releae 10.2.p02, but with G4FTFModel and residual nucleus
    excitation energy for diffraction set to 40 MeV.
    In G4VPartonStringModel, instead of having the string creation loop
    (with max 20 attempts) and the string fragmentation loop (with max
    100 attempts) separated, there is now one single loop for string
    creation and fragmentation, with max 1000 attempts, and in the case
    of failure a just-warning exception is thrown.
    Also, increased the number of max attempts to fragment strings from 10
    to 100 in G4ExcitedStringDecay.
- models/qmd (hadr-qmd-V10-02-01)
  o Set type of de-excitation channels to 'combined'.
- models/radioactive_decay (radioactive_decay-V10-02-13)
  o Fixed bug in G4RadioactiveDecay::LoadDecayTable(), to ignore IT decay
    when no entries are found in the database; fixed case of segmentation-fault
    due to attempted deletion of empty decay table.
- stopping (hadr-stopping-V10-02-02)
  o G4EmCaptureCascade: added c++11 keywords.
- util (hadr-util-V10-02-01)                                                 (*)
  o Fix in G4Nucleus::GetThermalNucleus() in branch on total energy 
    calculation using relativistic energy at higher energies.
    Addressing problem report #1911.

